cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.RO 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image and video object detection. It may also belong to the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories as it proposes a unified approach based on end-to-end learning of features. The paper may also be relevant to the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category as it deals with video analysis. Finally, it may belong to the robotics (cs.RO) sub-category as video object detection is important in practical scenarios such as autonomous driving.
